{"tid":142112,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個最黑仔嘅日子／事件","createTime":"2017-03-03T12:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T04:42:26.000Z","uid":1858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b257c2c606d32001d4a5b616bc8f4f9be6dba7e","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:59:10.000Z","msg":"背景：重感冒，個人溫溫鄧鄧<br />\n<br />\n以下事件係24小時內發生：<br />\n<br />\n某日<br />\n1.賭馬買左幾場一毫子都收唔番，最尾個場買左條四穿六，四隻熱門黎。最後當然唔中，仲要爆冷，四隻熱門都跑到冇曬影。<br />\n<br />\n2.比人票控罰錢：以前未試過，係咁啱個日第一次比人斷正<br />\n<br />\n3.行行下差一步比高空摘物打中，好似係底衫褲依架黎<br />\n<br />\n4.去atm㩒唔到錢（冇比人食卡，戶口本身亦都有錢）就係唔知點解拎唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢日令我諗起楊千嬅套行運超人，原來一個人黑起上黎真係咩事都會發生，仲要個人都運運鱷鱷on99咁"},{"pid":"7944f5add63a2d4594db7f3f5afc5a462bedc50c","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a75cdaba1e854b59b1ac57aa72e697e1761eca","tid":142112,"uid":28966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:13:05.000Z","msg":"試過連中三元<br />\n朝早跑步仆街跌斷腳要睇跌打<br />\n返屋企又比到門夾爆指甲爆哂缸<br />\n食野個時又辣親手指起水泡<br />\n痛到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9459cf940c3ed04e3678a7a6eef9f620b81bd7de","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過連中三元<br />\n朝早跑步仆街跌斷腳要睇跌打<br />\n返屋企又比到門夾爆指甲爆哂缸<br />\n食野個時又辣親手指起水泡<br />\n痛到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該痛到冇咩知覺"},{"pid":"c9d9c81ae59839e5d3ec90b5432ddb173f9317b0","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a89c085908fc2588236e4e1f6d41fac40253cc","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4a49b53f3af926e75cee05ee5425d47363117d","tid":142112,"uid":44456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"一世a0<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做人on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇優點 只有缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833adc2bc6d48e5ece5815b55709ea5963ee48de","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:49:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一世a0<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做人on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇優點 只有缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔好話一世，都未去<br />\n<br />\n咁睇都唔算黑仔丫，況且好多連登仔都係咁上下姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376ae3a2ef53f1138e146b519d663b81796cbf03","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:30:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a220c1a82c5e67e02a8b33bb7badbac3a4cc6d7","tid":142112,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過連中三元<br />\n朝早跑步仆街跌斷腳要睇跌打<br />\n返屋企又比到門夾爆指甲爆哂缸<br />\n食野個時又辣親手指起水泡<br />\n痛到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原本都唔記得咗，一睇到就諗返起，同你有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰日要返深圳office<br />\n行去的士站就俾個窿搞到扭親腫晒<br />\n喺公司去廁所開燈搞到斷甲，流晒血<br />\n捱到返香港坐巴士又俾人撞到仆低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267399081decdd3669cd2e214acb41d1ae5a692a","tid":142112,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:45:01.000Z","msg":"你都係黑一日啫<br />\n衰足幾年真係差少少頂唔順"},{"pid":"5d52a2a71f4dfebff9d19d1c093305d2d9abdd67","tid":142112,"uid":72481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"我試過朝早唔知醒差d遲到坐的士無左百五，上堂無帶書要吹水爆肚，放工第一次去中大上堂坐bus 訓到唔知醒過哂站，跑落地鐵行樓梯樓上有個細路扔蛋糕中我頭，最撚慘係落左堂嚴重腸胃炎，差d行唔到去廁所，而且過兩日行山比賽都行唔到"},{"pid":"507783a3357753f295713a54a24652bdc7651a67","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都係黑一日啫<br />\n衰足幾年真係差少少頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n黑足成日仲唔夠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衰足幾年個d應該同張家輝一樣比人搞過山墳"},{"pid":"98dbea3fef84d609c2f60a9a9f90d59131c35b8d","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過朝早唔知醒差d遲到坐的士無左百五，上堂無帶書要吹水爆肚，放工第一次去中大上堂坐bus 訓到唔知醒過哂站，跑落地鐵行樓梯樓上有個細路扔蛋糕中我頭，最撚慘係落左堂嚴重腸胃炎，差d行唔到去廁所，而且過兩日行山比賽都行唔到</blockquote><br />\n你呢到幾單wo,又唔係一日內"},{"pid":"dc4363babe81eb74da71759677f3bf6d217ac67e","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7495c9d1d48088aa10cad8170967405d371e4e9d","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce19a817a8199cae814ebc2620896db7eee8f8c8","tid":142112,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T04:42:26.000Z","msg":"冇曬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}